Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 05 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Rupture of extrinsic ligaments' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Lig. radiotriquetrum dorsale' radio button is enabled
And 'Lig. intercarpale dorsale' radio button is enabled

And 'Lig. radioscaphocapitatum' radio button is enabled
And 'Lig. radiolunotriquetrum' radio button is enabled
